This PowerShell script is designed for Windows Server 2022 to help you reduce unexpected interruptions when performing long-running tasks, by disabling automatic Windows Update installation and limiting system restarts initiated by update services. It does this by attempting to stop and modify the configuration of relevant services, scheduled tasks, and registry policies. It also adds status reporting to help you observe which operations succeed or fail.
